results.question: How many tracks are there?
results.gold_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM tracks;

results.question: List top 5 albums by track count
results.gold_sql: SELECT a.title, r.name, COUNT(t.id) AS track_count FROM albums a JOIN artists r ON a.artist_id = r.id LEFT JOIN tracks t ON t.album_id = a.id GROUP BY a.id ORDER BY track_count DESC LIMIT 5;

results.question: What is the total duration of all tracks?
results.gold_sql: SELECT SUM(duration) FROM tracks;

results.question: Show artists with more than 1 album
results.gold_sql: SELECT r.name, COUNT(a.id) FROM artists r LEFT JOIN albums a ON a.artist_id = r.id GROUP BY r.id HAVING COUNT(a.id) > 1;

results.question: List all rock tracks
results.gold_sql: SELECT name FROM tracks WHERE genre = 'Rock';

results.question: Which album has the longest track?
results.gold_sql: SELECT a.title, MAX(t.duration) FROM albums a JOIN tracks t ON t.album_id = a.id GROUP BY a.id ORDER BY MAX(t.duration) DESC LIMIT 1;

results.question: Count tracks per genre
results.gold_sql: SELECT genre, COUNT(*) FROM tracks GROUP BY genre;

results.question: Average track duration by genre
results.gold_sql: SELECT genre, AVG(duration) FROM tracks GROUP BY genre;

results.question: List albums released after 2015
results.gold_sql: SELECT title, year FROM albums WHERE year > 2015;

results.question: Find albums with more than 2 tracks
results.gold_sql: SELECT a.title, COUNT(t.id) AS cnt FROM albums a LEFT JOIN tracks t ON t.album_id = a.id GROUP BY a.id HAVING COUNT(t.id) > 2;

results.question: How many distinct genres exist?
results.gold_sql: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT genre) FROM tracks;
